{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "63HFB27UM5VOVJCE6W5RDD22MVQNL7JU",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041129004",
    "title": "ともに、前人未踏の未来へ",
    "enTitle": "Together, In To An Uncharted Future",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "もう、大丈夫です。\n……ごめんなさい、異国の地で迷惑かけちゃって。",
            "enText": "I'm fine now. \n……I'm sorry, for troubling you like this when we're overseas.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 229,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 263,
                    "pathId": -2024334611354400757
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -9140461857089127865
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 428,
                    "pathId": 5806609295672911710
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6444635062488086901,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "座り込んでしまったアーモンドアイをアイシングし、\nしばらく横にならせた。回復したのは、日も暮れた後だ。",
            "enText": "Almond Eye had nearly collapsed so we had her lay \ndown for a bit with some ice. It was nighttime \nby the time she seemed to have fully recovered.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4017456440225316853
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 428,
                    "pathId": -782017242569477545
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1515432394933640197,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "アーモンドアイの体は、触れてすぐわかるほど熱がこもっており、\nそれでいて、レース直後というのに汗の量が少なかった。",
            "enText": "Her body had been so overheated that it was noticeable \nto the touch. Even though it was immediately after \na race, she hadn't been sweating much at all.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君は、熱がこもりやすい体質なんだな",
                    "enText": "Seems like you get overheated easily",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方は、熱がこもりやすい体質なんだね",
                    "enText": "Seems like you get overheated easily",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 228,
                    "pathId": -4634004184263144020
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 428,
                    "pathId": 8293800270846051427
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5185322912128131954,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……はい。\nレースの後は特に、火照って倒れてしまうことがたまにあって。",
            "enText": "……Yes. Especially after races, \nI sometimes get so hot that I end up collapsing.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 230,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "た、倒れてしまうことが、たまにあった？",
                    "enText": "Y-you've collapsed before?",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 219,
                    "pathId": -5836234728953755129
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 234,
                    "pathId": -2461659449834347742
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 156,
                    "pathId": -563342539984107235
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4339201207609528214,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ええ……。そんなに頑丈じゃないんです。\n今回の渡航だって、気づいたら少し体重が落ちていましたし。",
            "enText": "Yes…… I'm not very resilient. Even during this \nexpedition, before I realized it, I had lost some weight.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 293,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……『頑丈じゃない』？君が？",
                    "enText": "……『Not resilient』? You're not?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "……『頑丈じゃない』？貴方が？",
                    "enText": "……『Not resilient』? You're not?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 319,
                    "pathId": 604867177861698924
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -2121468639878059893
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 411,
                    "pathId": -3231576055634567219
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2790292789172909354,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あんなにも激しいトレーニングで己を追い込み、\n海外リベンジもやり切ってしまった……彼女が？",
            "enText": "She pushed herself through that intense training and even \nmanaged to win her revenge match overseas……but she's frail?",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 204,
                    "pathId": 6222342016496724923
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 173,
                    "pathId": 3472190616200579623
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 411,
                    "pathId": 8508351106350022024
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5174803872678751138,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はい。レースの後はなるべくすぐにシャワーを浴びるように\nしたりして、自分なりに対策はしているんですけれど。",
            "enText": "Yes. I try to take a shower as soon as I can after a race, \nand I do try to do what I can to prevent it from happening.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 270,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……そう、だったのか……",
                    "enText": "……So you have……",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "……そう、だったんだ……",
                    "enText": "……So you have……",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -1155305489184267683
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 2283990439666072637
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 315,
                    "pathId": 2720823365827431810
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2845611040223825532,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "てっきりフィジカルもメンタルも凄まじい子なのかと思っていた。\n――いや、フィジカルが素晴らしいことに間違いはない。",
            "enText": "I thought she was physically and mentally strong. \n——No, there's no doubt her physical condition is amazing.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 212,
                    "pathId": -1117327112930528453
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 5518669318445817549
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 17,
                    "pathId": 4561626051358610844
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2073119976443915014,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "が、特に、凄まじく稀有で頑強なのはメンタルで、\nそれをもって、体をハイレベルに叩き上げていたのだ。",
            "enText": "But, what was more astounding was her mental strength. \nThat was the reason she was able to train herself to this level.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 7273250436318906933
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1907672417249600824
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2728017309549615120,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "並大抵のメンタルではない。\n非常に稀有で、奇特で、怪物のような心の強さだ。",
            "enText": "It wasn't ordinary by any stretch of the imagination. \nIt was incredibly rare, an extraordinary strength of mind.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": 1387831858993461021
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": -2692740618189938977
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 170,
                    "pathId": 6472872769712966035
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4663482421362445586,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女であればトリプルティアラや、海外GⅠ制覇、世界レコード……\nいや、もしかするとそれ以上の偉業にも――",
            "enText": "Someone like her could win the Triple Tiara, win an overseas G1, and \neven break a World Record…… No, maybe even something more amazing——",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（その相方に、俺が……）",
                    "enText": "(To a partner like that, I will……)",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（その相方に、私が……）",
                    "enText": "(To a partner like that, I will……)",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": 429276572290853268
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 163,
                    "pathId": 7631486410292685528
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 170,
                    "pathId": -308222293743404652
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8348223136131653339,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "――だから、もっと強くなりたいんです。心も、体も。\nこれからもやろうと決めたことを、必ずやり遂げられるように。",
            "enText": "——That's why I want to get stronger. In mind, and body. \nTo be able to accomplish whatever I set out to do.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 375,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（――いや、……俺が？）",
                    "enText": "(——No……I will?)",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（――いや、……私が？）",
                    "enText": "(——No……I will?)",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -8034112569840365695
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -9000736763616819848
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 386,
                    "pathId": -7294526815793059029
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6127967169412728650,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あまりに、レベルが合わない。\nそう思えるほど、アーモンドアイは輝いていた。",
            "enText": "Our levels are just too different. Almond Eye's \nbrilliance was such that I couldn't help but think that.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": -3667442389672175300
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 147,
                    "pathId": -900166979258873969
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 6242254769715985854
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7131342255162733770,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "新人トレーナー",
            "enName": "Rookie Trainer",
            "jpText": "へー、1着だったあの子いいじゃん。スプリンター志望かな。\nアタシあとで声かけてみよーっと。",
            "enText": "OhhーThat girl that placed first is good. Maybe she's planning \nto be a Sprinter? I'll try talking to her afterwards.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 215,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": 1629148017324346997
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": -5154622973640801016
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3648064551447843358,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "帰国し、元の毎日が戻ってきた。担当ウマ娘を探すため、\n模擬レースを回り、教官とのトレーニングを見学する――",
            "enText": "After returning home, life returns to normal. To find a partner Uma \nMusume, watching mock races and observing training with instructors——",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -7279336310308654808,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "トレセン学園へ入学するウマ娘は全員才能あるウマ娘。\n素晴らしい結果を残すであろう子は多くいた。けれど。",
            "enText": "All the Uma Musume who enter Tracen Academy are talented. \nThere were many who could go on to achieve great things. But……",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（……ダメだ、忘れられない）",
                    "enText": "(……I can't stop thinking about it)",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8481078511319254727,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "気晴らしに遠出し、海岸近くの裏道を散歩することにした。\nかすかな波の音と潮の香りが心地よい。",
            "enText": "For a change of pace, I decided to take a walk \nalong a backroad along the coast. The sound of the \nwaves and faint smell of the ocean were soothing.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -1309067586849878817,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……と。",
            "enText": "……Oh.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -1793903593778256036,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "一匹の蝶が、力なく舞う姿があった。\n既視感に、思わず追いかけると……広い、砂浜に出た。",
            "enText": "A butterfly fluttered weakly by. Feeling a sense of déjà vu, \nI followed after it……and ended up on a wide, sandy beach.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -5281700724062980056,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はぁあああっ！！！",
            "enText": "Haaaaaaa!!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 41,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "！",
                    "enText": "!",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7924524379400310425,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はぁっ、はぁっ、はぁっ！\n……――ふふっ！　ふふふっ！　たぁあああっ！！",
            "enText": "Haa, haa, haa! \n……——Fufuu! Fufufuu! Taaaaaa!!",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 206,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5304886124849621741
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -1589308740505249411
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2139041451264477107,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "しなやかに砂をかく。体が、尾が、躍動している。\n水平線のきらめきを追うように、彼女はまっすぐに走っていた。",
            "enText": "Her feet effortlessly moved through the sand, her tail swishing \nabout. She ran straight ahead, chasing after the sparkling horizon.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……やっぱり、すごいな",
                    "enText": "……She really is amazing",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 247,
                    "pathId": -3653928280543194534
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6135781852226681243,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あの日々が、重なるように脳裏を駆け抜けていく。\n瑞々しい瞳で駆け抜ける姿。妥協なく己を叩き上げる横顔。",
            "enText": "The days we spent together flashed through my mind. \nHer bright eyes as she ran. The profile of someone \nwho pushed themself to the limit, never letting up.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 266,
                    "pathId": 3368972634374308231
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2211117945888614930,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "当然のように果たした、高らかな宣言。\n恐れさえ生まれた、異様な勝利への執念――",
            "enText": "A bold declaration as she cleared her goal. \nAn obsession with victory that could be intimidating——",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 253,
                    "pathId": 2772104430799448386
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4189390022345967078,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あらゆる未来がそこにある。そのすべてが輝いている。\n――胸が熱くなり、涙が零れた。",
            "enText": "The myriad futures that could be hers. Each of them shining \nbrightly. ——My heart felt heavy as I could feel tears welling up.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（その未来を……見たい）",
                    "enText": "(I want to……see those futures)",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 181,
                    "pathId": 4489565004414574370
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 205,
                    "pathId": -1109680894924616022
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 198,
                    "pathId": 5298972398951134158
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7063503901848486497,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女ならば、できないことはない。\nそう思わせる程の、輝きが――アーモンドアイにはあるのだ！",
            "enText": "There was nothing she couldn't accomplish. \nAlmond Eye's sparkle was so bright it could make you believe that!",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（その未来を、俺が支えたい！）",
                    "enText": "(I want to support that future!)",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（その未来を、私が支えたい！）",
                    "enText": "(I want to support that future!)",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 2438357517774531455
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 471236626423048281
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 198,
                    "pathId": -5264615438188339464
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2659789964221498706,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はぁ、はぁ……ふー……。――あっ、偶然ですね！\nまさかこんなところで会えるなんて……ちょうどよかった！",
            "enText": "Haa, haa……phew-…… ——Ah, what a coincidence! \nTo think I'd be able to meet you here……it's perfect timing!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 364,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 188,
                    "pathId": 2701460975365034694
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 526139683548442074
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": 6435739775756306568
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3406789191348778328,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "わたし、今貴方にすごく会いたかったんです！",
            "enText": "I really wanted to see you again!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 116,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "お、俺に？",
                    "enText": "M-me?",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "わ、私に？",
                    "enText": "M-me?",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 8537922276702913718
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3528078971222322639,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ええ！　たった今、これを試していたところで。",
            "enText": "Yes! Just now, I was trying this out.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
