            "pathId": 4301622741011758839,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "と、彼女が取り出し、示したタブレットに映っていたのは、\n以前彼女に間違えて渡したフォーム案の『ver.1』だった。",
            "enText": "She pulled out her tablet and showed it to me. It was \nthe 『ver.1』 draft that I had sent her by mistake before.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "これを……？",
                    "enText": "This……?",
                    "nextBlock": 31
