            ],
            "pathId": 1210207251125298236,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "初めて見た時、未完成品だなんて思いませんでした。\n正直、『ver.9』との違いも些細なものでしたし。",
            "enText": "The first time I saw it, I didn't realize it was unfinished. To be \nhonest, I thought the difference between it and 『ver.9』 were minor.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 307,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": -8139065065018646911
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 172,
                    "pathId": 2290022191167479911
