        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "でも、実際に走ってみると全く違いました！\n『ver.9』に比べて、想像以上に体に馴染まなくて。",
            "enText": "But, after trying them out personally, it was completely different! \nCompared to 『ver.9』 it didn't feel as natural as I expected.",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 274,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 192,
                    "pathId": -2883232035745796030
