            "pathId": 5355540086293660802,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……徹底したからこそ、生まれた結果ですね。あの日、\n寝ていなかったんですよね？　覚えているんです、お顔が真っ青で。",
            "enText": "……This is the result of your thorough revisions, \nisn't it? That day, you didn't get much sleep \ndid you? I remember just how pale your face was.",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 392,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 260,
                    "pathId": 7444513464163219889
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8766975503073849440
