            "pathId": -4007445978764304518,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……わたしは誰にも負けたくないけれど、\n貴方はなにより、自分に負けたくないんですね。だから――",
            "enText": "……I don't want to lose to anyone but, for you, above all else, \nyou don't want to lose to yourself do you? That's why——",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 294,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "animData": [
