            "blockIdx": 36
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "思わぬ展開に気が動転する。本当はスカウトを躊躇う程に、\nその強さに惚れ込んでいたと、伝えたいのに言葉が紡げない――",
            "enText": "I was caught off guard by the sudden turn of events. \nTruthfully, her strength made me hesitate to scout her. \nI wanted to tell her, but I just couldn't put it in to words——",
            "nextBlock": 38,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……っ、君なら何でもできると思っている",
                    "enText": "……I think you can achieve anything",
                    "nextBlock": 38
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "……っ、貴方なら何でもできると思ってる",
                    "enText": "……I think you can achieve anything",
                    "nextBlock": 38
                }
