            ],
            "pathId": 918703722663425423,
            "blockIdx": 39
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――前人未踏の、夢にすら。……気づけば、彼女に問うていた。",
            "enText": "Something unprecedented, beyond imagination……\nBefore I realized it, I was already asking her.",
            "nextBlock": 41,
