            "pathId": 2174130387335774096,
            "blockIdx": 41
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう、誰も成し遂げたものはいない。\nだからこそ、その答えが解るのなら――",
            "enText": "Right, something that nobody has ever done before. \nTherefore, if you had the answer——",
