            "pathId": -7421258851352610679,
            "blockIdx": 42
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……方法なんてわからないわ。わたしにはわからない。\nでも、逆に、そもそもどうしてできないって思うの？",
            "enText": "……I don't know how. I don't know the answer. \nBut, on the other hand, why do you think it's not possible?",
            "nextBlock": 44,
