            "pathId": 5034368352123085601,
            "blockIdx": 43
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "全力で戦って、必ず勝てばいいのよ。\nそれを8回やればいい。7勝も8勝も変わらないわ。",
            "enText": "You just have to fight with your full strength and win. Just do \nthat 8 times. There's not much difference between 7 and 8 victories.",
