            "pathId": -6854796435116183796,
            "blockIdx": 44
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "常識を捻じ曲げ続けた日々から生まれた――\n軽やかで、確かな、自信。",
            "enText": "It was the answer of someone who spent their days \nbreaking common sense——Light, certain, confident.",
            "nextBlock": 46,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（もしかしたら、こういうウマ娘が――）",
                    "enText": "(Maybe this is the kind of Uma Musume——)",
                    "nextBlock": 46
