            "pathId": -8246711639992100837,
            "blockIdx": 47
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……。\nそういえば、海を渡る蝶もいるって話を聞いたことがあるわ。",
            "enText": "……That reminds me. \nButterflies that cross the ocean, I've heard stories about them.",
            "nextBlock": 49,
