            "blockIdx": 48
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "蝶の羽は、柔らかくて、小さなもの。\nけれど……海を渡れやしないだなんて誰にわかるの？",
            "enText": "A butterfly's wings are soft, and tiny. But…… \nHow do you know if they wouldn't be able to cross the ocean?",
            "nextBlock": 50,
